    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1910-06-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1910-06-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="510"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d510">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Brazilian Chargé</gloss>.</hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d510fn1">Same to Argentine chargé.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-06-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 10, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Chargé d’Affaires</hi>: I beg to inclose for
                    your information a copy of an aide-mémoire<note n="2" xml:id="d510fn2"
                        >Supra.</note> which was handed to the chargé d’affaires ad interim of Chile
                    on the 1st instant and a copy of an aide-mémoire,<note n="2" xml:id="d510fn3"
                        >Supra.</note> which was addressed to the diplomatic representatives of
                    Ecuador and Peru at this capital on the same day, in reference to the mediation
                    between Peru and Ecuador for the settlement of their differences in connection
                    with the arbitration of their conflicting boundary claims.</p>
                <p>These aides-mémoire have been communicated by cable to the American embassy at
                    Petropolis, for communication to your Government.</p>
                <p>I am, my dear Mr. de Lima, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Huntington Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
